PHP Version Incompatibility When opening the installer (http://51.20.136.144/install/): Error  : PrestaShop requires PHP 8.1 8.4, but server was running PHP 8.5.1. 
Solution  : - Installed compatible PHP 8.2 + required extensions:  sudo dnf install php8.2 php8.2-fpm php8.2-mysqlnd php8.2-gd php8.2-intl php8.2-mbstring php8.2-xml php8.2-curl php8.2-zip -y  
- Restarted services:  sudo systemctl restart httpd php-fpm  
Installer page now loaded correctly. 



Missing PHP Extensions Installer system compatibility check failed with: 
- GD library missing 
- PDO MySQL not loaded 
- Intl extension missing 
Solution :  sudo dnf install php8.2-gd php8.2-intl php8.2-mysqlnd -y sudo systemctl restart httpd  All checks turned green. 

RDS Database Setup 

Created RDS MySQL instance: - Engine: MySQL 
- Instance class: db.t3.micro (Free Tier) - Public access: Yes (for simplicity during setup) 
- Database name: prestashop - Username: puser 
Struggles & Fixes  : - Connection failed  : Can't connect to MySQL server 
Access denied 

Causes  : 
1. RDS security group did not allow port 3306 from EC2 security group 
2. Database name mismatch
3. Initial public access misconfiguration Solutions  : - Added inbound rule to RDS security group: MySQL (3306) from EC2 security group ID 
- Verified RDS endpoint, DB name, user, password in installer 
After fixes installer connected successfully and created tables 





Installation Timeout During final installation steps: 
Cause  : Low memory on t2.micro during heavy operations (table creation, cache, modules). 
Solution : 
- Added swap space (2 GB)
- Tuned PHP-FPM for low memory
Refreshed page after timeout → installation had completed in background. 

8. Post-Installation Issues & Fixes 
- 500 Internal Server Error in back office → enabled debug mode ( _PS_MODE_DEV_ = true ) + cleared cache ( rm -rf /var/www/html/var/cache/  ) + fixed permissions.
 - 404 Not Found on admin URL → used full path  /index.php  to access login → regenerated .htaccess. 
- Renamed admin folder to  admin_mystore_1771494920  for security. 
- Deleted install  folder. 




